# Save the Asteroids as Agent Q! 🚀✨
Protect the precious Galaxy Orb, scattered across miniature planets, from the notorious space pirate Tumai!

[media]
[media]
[media]
[media]
[media]

Space pirate Tumai is causing chaos across the peaceful asteroids!

As an elite B.A.R.D. agent, you must:
- Explore 60+ vibrant dioramas
- Interact with adorable asteroid locals
- Spot hidden objects to track down the Tumai
- Master puzzles and rhythm challenges for ultimate rewards

With 4 unique space themes to explore and growing collections, the adventure evolves with every mission!

The galaxy needs Agent Q! Will you answer the call? 🕵️‍♂️🌌
